
@{
    ViewBag.Title = "FAQ";
}

<h2>FAQ</h2>
<div class="container">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="card card-body bg-light">
            <h5>Will food be provided for the team?</h5>
            <p>
                Snacks and meals will be provided at some practices and 
                competitions. For other events, the teammates will be required 
                to bring their own food/money. To view event specific 
                information, please refer to the Events Page.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="card card-body bg-light">
            <h5>How do I know which outfit is which?</h5>
            <p>
                Clicking on the name of an outfit from the event details page 
                will take you to an image of that outfit. All of the outfits 
                and there names can be viewed here.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="card card-body bg-light">
            <h5>Where can I find contact information for the other parent volunteers?</h5>
            <p>
                Phone numbers and email addresses for each volunteer can be 
                found here if the volunteer chose to make that information 
                public. Otherwise, they may be contacted using VolunCheer's 
                Chat service.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="card card-body bg-light">
            <h5>How do I know what my responsibilities are as a volunteer?</h5>
            <p>
                You will review alert notifications via text/email according 
                to your preferences whenever as task is assigned to you. All 
                of your currently assigned tasks can be viewed by clicking 
                Dashboard on the menu bar.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
